pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/markets/rates-bonds/asian-bonds-attract-hefty-inflows-us-rate-outlook-strong-exports-2024-08-14/</guid></item><item><title>经济出现新的疲软迹象，中国官员没有喘息的机会</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/markets/asia/no-respite-chinese-officials-economy-shows-new-signs-weakness-2024-08-14/</link><description>最近一系列惨淡的指标降低了人们对 7 月份中国经济表现的预期，这对 2024 年剩余时间来说是一个不祥的迹象，并表明除了缓解世界第二大经济体的痛点之外，还需要采取更多刺激措施。</description><pubDate>Wed, 14 Aug 2024 07:09:32 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/markets/asia/no-respite-chinese-officials-economy-shows-new-signs-weakness-2024-08-14/</guid></item><item><title>中国调查殡仪馆和服务机构中猖獗的腐败行为</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/world/china/china-probes-rampant-graft-funeral-homes-services-2024-08-14/</link><description>官方媒体周三称，中国揭露了殡葬服务行业普遍存在的腐败现象，殡仪馆的长期管理人员和官员犯下非法收费和乱建墓地等违法行为。</description><pubDate>Wed, 14 Aug 2024 05:46:57 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/world/china/china-probes-rampant-graft-funeral-homes-services-2024-08-14/</guid></item><item><title>新加坡丰益国际 (Wilmar) 因食品部门实力强劲而实现高收益利润，阿达尼丰益 (Adani Wilmar) 盈利增加</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/business/retail-consumer/singapores-wilmar-posts-higher-hy-profit-food-unit-strength-higher-adani-wilmar-2024-08-14/</link><description>新加坡农业企业丰益国际 (Wilmar International) 上半年利润小幅上涨，反映出其食品业务表现较好，并受益于阿达尼丰益 (Adani Wilmar) 合资企业盈利增加。</description><pubDate>Wed, 14 Aug 2024 04:47:34 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/business/retail-consumer/singapores-wilmar-posts-higher-hy-profit-food-unit-strength-higher-adani-wilmar-2024-08-14/</guid></item><item><title>早上竞价：欢迎来到切割俱乐部，新西兰人</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/markets/global-markets-view-europe-2024-08-14/</link><description>Stella Qiu 展望欧洲和全球市场未来一天</description><pubDate>Wed, 14 Aug 2024 04:33:31 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/markets/global-markets-view-europe-2024-08-14/</guid></item><item><title>日本首相岸田下台的反应</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/world/china/reactions-japans-pm-kishida-stepping-down-2024-08-14/</link><description>日本首相岸田文雄表示，他将于九月下台，结束因政治丑闻而受损的三年任期，并为新首相应对物价上涨的影响铺平道路。</description><pubDate>Wed, 14 Aug 2024 04:02:45 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/world/china/reactions-japans-pm-kishida-stepping-down-2024-08-14/</guid></item><item><title>新西兰降息，亚洲股市上涨，新西兰股市下跌</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/markets/global-markets-wrapup-1-2024-08-14/</link><description>亚洲股市周三上涨，此前疲软的美国生产者价格数据激发了人们对消费者价格通胀温和的希望，而新西兰央行自 2020 年初以来首次降息后，新西兰元下跌。</description><pubDate>Wed, 14 Aug 2024 02:40:25 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/markets/global-markets-wrapup-1-2024-08-14/</guid></item><item><title>日本首相岸田将辞职，为新领导人铺平道路</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/world/japan/japan-pm-kishida-wont-run-re-election-ldp-race-kyodo-reports-2024-08-14/</link><description>日本首相岸田文雄表示，他将于下个月辞职，屈服于公众对政治丑闻和生活成本上涨的不满，这些都损害了他的三年任期，并引发了一场接替他的竞争。</description><pubDate>Wed, 14 Aug 2024 01:34:34 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/world/japan/japan-pm-kishida-wont-run-re-election-ldp-race-kyodo-reports-2024-08-14/</guid></item><item><title>美国通胀数据良好后美元下跌；新西兰元因降息而下滑</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/markets/currencies/dollar-droops-after-benign-inflation-data-kiwi-firm-before-rbnz-decision-2024-08-14/</link><description>美元兑主要货币隔夜暴跌后，周三仍处于不利地位，因美国生产者价格的良好数据增强了对美联储今年降息的押注。</description><pubDate>Wed, 14 Aug 2024 00:44:03 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/markets/currencies/dollar-droops-after-benign-inflation-data-kiwi-firm-before-rbnz-decision-2024-08-14/</guid></item><item><title>阿尔加拉法、山东队晋级亚冠联赛</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/sports/soccer/al-gharafa-shandong-secure-berths-asian-champions-league-elite-2024-08-14/</link><description>卡塔尔的阿尔加拉法队和中国的山东泰山队在周五的新亚冠联赛小组赛抽签中占据了剩下的两个席位，周二的附加赛分别战胜了沙巴布·阿赫利队和曼谷联队。</description><pubDate>Wed, 14 Aug 2024 00:30:14 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/sports/soccer/al-gharafa-shandong-secure-berths-asian-champions-league-elite-2024-08-14/</guid></item><item><title>加州允许中国机器人出租车公司文远知行进行乘客测试</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/business/autos-transportation/california-allows-chinese-robotaxi-firm-weride-test-with-passengers-2024-08-13/</link><description>根据加州公用事业监管机构的许可，中国自动驾驶初创公司文远知行已获得加州批准，可以测试其无人驾驶汽车载客。</description><pubDate>Tue, 13 Aug 2024 23:47:37 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/business/autos-transportation/california-allows-chinese-robotaxi-firm-weride-test-with-passengers-2024-08-13/</guid></item><item><title>路透调查显示日本8月份商业信心因中国经济放缓而下滑</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/markets/asia/japans-business-sentiment-aug-slips-chinas-slowdown-2024-08-13/</link><description>路透短观月度调查周三发现，日本制造商对 8 月份商业状况的信心略有下降，服务业情绪有所缓和，原因是中国需求低迷打压了企业信心。</description><pubDate>Tue, 13 Aug 2024 23:04:49 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/markets/asia/japans-business-sentiment-aug-slips-chinas-slowdown-2024-08-13/</guid></item></channel></rss>